casebody.data:
IN RE GEORGE F. S236397 Supreme Court of California November 9, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

In light of the dismissal of the juvenile's wardship petition pursuant to Welfare and Institutions Code section 786, his motion to dismiss review in this court is granted.
